{"tid":1091874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 兩政黨今日(4日)到政府總部請願，不滿$4000處理緩慢","createTime":"2019-04-04T12:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T03:11:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f691555e6eedaef5a655289740c825de221facf5","tid":1091874,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T12:02:48.000Z","msg":"關愛共享計劃派4000港元頻甩轆，逾百萬申請者遞交表格後仍未接獲確認通知，造成恐慌。兩政黨今日(4日)到政府總部請願，不滿在職家庭津貼辦事處處理緩慢，要求加快處理申請程序，並延長截止申請日期、增加領取支票的地點。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯北區支部30多名成員到政總抗議，北區區議員曾興隆指，各區辦事處代巿民收集近2000份表格，有兩夫婦或家人同時遞交表格，只有一人接獲確認通知，令申請者疑惑。10多名新民主同盟成員亦到政總請願，批評計劃混亂兼擾民，指當局低估申請人數，議員辦事處接獲多名市民對資訊發放及發放款項程序的投訴。<br />\n<br />\n兩個政黨均建議當局增撥資源，增聘人員處理申請，並要求政府延長接受申請期限。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190404/bkn-20190404162623271-0404_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=402882b067c08fd401687387b89c53c3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190404%2Fbkn-20190404162623271-0404_00822_001.html%3Feventsection%3Dhk_news%26eventid%3D402882b067c08fd401687387b89c53c3&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvDDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=d9a5c3e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190404/bkn-20190404162623271-0404_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=402882b067c08fd401687387b89c53c3</a>"},{"pid":"43d62c64bcfeee0e8df34e60f4c07a9fc49d3e70","tid":1091874,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T12:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190404/photo/bkn-20190404162623271-0404_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190404180637\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190404%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190404162623271-0404_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190404180637&h=3ab26e36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0547ae063522a59f6d1a095767d81bca5d22dd86","tid":1091874,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T12:03:19.000Z","m